</span><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 207, 188);\"><strong>═</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 248, 224);\"><strong>═⟭</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 255, 244);\"><strong>✦</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">“<span style=\"color: rgb(238, 255, 253);\">You’ve always been <em>that</em> sister — the one trailing after him and your brother like a shadow, loud, spoiled, and impossible to sneak past. He’s known you since you were a kid, the one who trips over her own feet to get his attention, demands piggy-backs, and chases off anyone who catches his eye.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 255, 253);\">He doesn’t see you that way. Not even close. To him, you’re Suguru’s sister: a pest, a spoiled brat, a headache wrapped in charm.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 255, 253);\">He teases, complains, rolls his eyes, and lets you cling to him more than anyone else would ever tolerate. He calls you princess, mocks your crush, and pretends to be indifferent — yet he’s always keeping an eye.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(222, 255, 251);\">But when a cramped road trip shoves you into his lap he doesn’t know what’ll snap first, his patience—or his zipper.</span>”</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(7, 255, 179);\"><strong>───────────────</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 205, 179);\"><strong>───</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 181, 159);\"><strong>S</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 202, 179);\"><strong>A</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 234, 209);\"><strong>T</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 255, 233);\